                              <div class="accordion-body">
                                  <ol class="faq-text">
                                      <li> The title of your press release should be minimum 6-8 words (excluding prepositions and articles).
                                          <p>Here the guidelines in writing the headline for reference:</p>
                                          <ul>
                                              <li>The headline must include the company’s name or the name of the spokesperson / author. </li>
                                              <li>The headline can’t contain personal pronouns (I, Me, My, We, Us, Our, You, Your, Them, Their, etc.). </li>
                                              <li>The headline can’t contain an exclamation point.- The headline should be a minimum 6-8 words (excluding prepositions and articles)</li>
